    <li>Conduct literature review of existing research</li>
    <li>Design experimental methodology and protocols</li>
    <li>Collect and analyze data using statistical methods</li>
    <li>Prepare manuscript for peer review</li>
  </ul>
</div>
```

## Minimal Lists

Clean, minimal styling:

```css
